title: Animal Illustrations
content:
Hi all.   
   
I'm looking for a good source of animal illustrations that   
look like letterpress cuts, or rubberstamps (relatively thick   
line art). Two examples of what I'm talking about are:   
   
 [http://www.ing.com](http://web.archive.org/web/20131018033346/http:/www.ing.com/)   
 [http://www.brooksbrothers.com](http://web.archive.org/web/20131018033346/http:/www.brooksbrothers.com/)   
   
I've seen the cuts at Briar Press, similar, but are there other   
sources for this kind of thing, pref. online?   
   
Thanks,   
Randy
author: aquatoad
